                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170917-128-defend904 t18170917-128-punish641"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>. Aged 26.</p>
               <p>SMITH - <rs id="t18170917-128-verdict642" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18170917-128-verdict642" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. - <rs id="t18170917-128-punish643" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18170917-128-punish643" type="punishmentCategory" value="death"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170917-128-defend905 t18170917-128-punish643"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>. Aged 17.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Justice Burrough.</p>
